quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  27,36,"jab ( qasid ) Sulaiman ke paas pouncha to Sulaiman ne kahakiya tum mujhe maal se madad dena chahtay ho, jo kuch khuda ne mujhe ataa farmaya hai woh is se behtar hai jo tumhe diya hai haqeeqat yeh hai ke tum hi apne tohfay se khush hotay hogay"
  27,37,un ke paas wapas jao hum un par aisay lashkar se hamla karen ge jis ke muqablay ki un mein taaqat nah hogi aur un ko wahan se be izzat karkay nikaal den ge aur woh zaleel hon ge
  27,38,Sulaiman ne kaha ke ae darbaar walo! koi tum mein aisa hai ke qabal is ke ke woh log farmanbardar ho kar hamaray paas ayen malka ka takhat mere paas le aeye
  27,39,jaanat mein se aik quwwat hekal jin ne kaha ke qabal is ke ke aap apni jagah se utheen mein is ko aap ke paas la hazir karta hon aur mein is ( ke uthany ki ) taaqat rakhta hon ( aur ) amanat daar hon
  27,40,1 shakhs jis ko kitaab Ellahi ka ilm tha kehnay laga ke mein aap ki aankhh ke jhapkane se pehlay pehlay usay aap ke paas haazir kiye deta hon. jab Sulaiman ne takhat ko apne paas rakha howa dekha to kaha ke yeh mere perwar-digaar ka fazl hai taakay mujhe aazamaa_e ke mein shukar karta hon ya kufran Nemat karta hon aur jo shukar karta hai to apne hi faiday ke liye shukar karta hai aur jo nashukri karta hai to mera perwar-digaar be parwa ( aur ) karam karne wala hai
  27,41,Sulaiman ne kaha ke malka ke ( imthehaan aqal ke ) liye is ke takhat ki soorat badal do. dekhen ke woh soojh rakhti hai ya un logon mein hai jo soojh nahi rakhtay
  27,42,jab woh aa pohanchi to poocha gaya kekiya aap ka takhat bhi isi terhan ka hai? is ne kaha ke yeh to goya ho baho wohi hai aur hum ko is se pehlay hi ( Sulaiman ki Azmat shaan ) ka ilm hogaya tha aur hum farmanbardar hain
  27,43,"aur woh jo khuda ke siwa ( aur ki ) parastish karti thi, Sulaiman ne is ko is se manakiya ( is se pehlay to ) woh kafiroon mein se thi"
  27,44,"( phir ) is se kaha gaya ke mehal mein chaliye, jab is ne is ( ke farsh ) ko dekha to usay pani ka hoz samgha aur ( kapra utha kar ) apni pindliyan khol den. Sulaiman ne kaha yeh aisa mehal hai jis mein ( neechay bhi ) sheeshay jurey hue hain. woh bol uthi ke perwar-digaar mein apne aap par zulm karti rahi thi aur ( ab ) mein Sulaiman ke haath par khuday-e rab alaalmin par imaan latayen hon"
